column1: Table containing the significantly differentially expressed genes. The columns include
baseMean = the average of the normalized counts taken over all samples
log2FoldChange = log2 fold change between the groups. E.g. value 2 means that the expression has increased 4-fold
lfcSE = standard error of the log2FoldChange estimate
Reference:  M Love, W Huber and S Anders: Moderated estimation of fold change and dispersion for RNA-Seq data with DESeq2. Genome Biol. 2014 15:550
